Jangan khawatir.  Oke?  Ya.

00:09:27.080 --> 00:09:28.240
Dokter Veer!

00:09:30.600 --> 00:09:32.880
Dokter Veer!  Berhenti!  Dokter Veer!

00:09:34.680 --> 00:09:37.880
Veer akan menemui Rani, dan
